cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.PL 

The paper discusses the design of self-adaptive software systems, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). It also mentions feedback control loops, which are commonly used in control systems (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the issue of multiple control loops, which is related to distributed computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper proposes a set of design patterns, which is relevant to programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
